DC Diner on the corner of 13th Street and H Street NE is a diner with a big menu and cheerful and compact seating. The menu includes everything one expects from a diner in terms of breakfasts, ongoing daytime food, snacks and comfort food, in addition to late night munchies. This area has a choice of eateries to suit different wallets and surely persists for good reason in an end of town that seems to attract more interest. The cafe sports the most unique ATM I have ever seen.
